response.original_title: Rock House: Metal Guitar - Leads, Runs and Rhythms Level 2
response.overview: Talented guitarist Dan Jacobs, of the metalcore band Atreyu, leads developing guitar players through this advanced lesson, which covers lead techniques such as tapping, hammer-ons, pull-offs, palm muting, scales, arpeggios, seed picking and more. Using several of his band's hit songs as examples, Jacobs demonstrates complete leads, guitar harmony sections, melodic metal rhythm and lead patterns, and more.
response.title: Rock House: Metal Guitar - Leads, Runs and Rhythms Level 2
